0.description: Betty started living with Joel six years ago.

1.description: Betty enjoys planting crops and tending to them.

2.description: Betty wishes that she and her boyfriend Joel could afford to buy a few horses.

3.description: Betty wishes she didn't have to travel to the nearby town often.

5.description: When Betty feels overwhelmed, she lies down on her bed and listens to ASMR through her noise-cancelling headphones.

6.description: Betty wants to have a child, hopefully a daughter, but Joel told her years ago that he didn't want children.

7.description: Joel and Betty saw strange lights in the skies in the 11th of May of 2023.

8.description: On the 11th of May of 2023, the local news broadcast was cut off in the middle of a transmission as they were reporting on the strange lights in the sky.

9.description: Joel and Betty have heard ominous explosions in the distance throughout the morning of the 12th of May of 2023.

10.description: Saturday May 13 of 2023, 9 AM. Betty is going to talk to Joel about their conflicting desires regarding having a child and try to come to a mutual understanding or compromise. The duration of this action is not specified in the given information. It can vary based on the discussion and resolution reached by Betty and Joel.
